From 5734f0cd27c94514910cfa0e2a13b8998e2387b9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 11:32:29 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 30/73] Activate PDF extension pages

The viewer knocked with private keys,
But no one blessed its Chrome-ish ways.
One helper call now lights the hall,
And Mojo shows the next brick wall.
